What is AgentsAI?

AgentsAI is a dynamic platform merging AI technology with blockchain to create, launch, and trade autonomous AI agents. With AgentsAI, users can develop personalized AI agents that engage with communities, automate tasks, and even launch their own tokens. From an AI agent marketplace to a toolkit of powerful AI solutions, AgentsAI empowers users to monetize and scale digital interactions, making decentralized, intelligent agents accessible for business and entertainment alike.

What is the Utility of the $AGENT Token?

The $AGENT token offers staking rewards, including airdrops of AI agent memecoins and tokens launched on the Agent Platform, giving stakers a share of each new project. Additionally, revenue from the AI Marketplace and AI Agent Marketplace funds regular token buybacks and burns, enhancing token value and scarcity.
